Package: bSCDCsampler
Type: Package
Title: Gibbs sampler of "Decoding Neuronal Ensembles from Spatially-Referenced Calcium Traces: A Bayesian Semiparametric Approach"
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2026-03-16
