Maintainer: Laura D'Angelo <laura.dangelo@unimib.it>
Description: The package contains the Gibbs sampler to sample from the posterior
    distribution of the parameters of the model of D'Angelo, Denti, Canale and Guindani
    (2026) "Decoding Neuronal Ensembles from Spatially-Referenced Calcium Traces: 
    A Bayesian Semiparametric Approach". The method performs the simultaneous
    deconvolution of calcium traces and clustering of neurons based on the underlying
    spiking activity. 
